@node "InstallUse" "Installation and Usage"
@next "Distribution"
@prev "Requirements"
@{b}Here's how you install GrabScreen onto your system:@{ub}

 @{b}1)@{ub} Copy Grabscreen and Guide in some directory.

 @{b}2)@{ub} Click twise on GrabScreen icon.
 
 Usage:

 @{b}1)@{ub} Run program and select screen.After this select
             output filename.

 @{b}2)@{ub} Close before save - Close window before saving.


